{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"006c0bc054","title":"中央首长与“毛泽东思想红卫兵首都兵团”座谈纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da84798924","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":4,"articleId":"006c0bc054","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"阎长贵","id":"269c664f91","type":"人物"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"穆欣","id":"6767f054ce","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢镗忠","id":"70f74b01a1","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"王任重","id":"8b05ac46d8","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"周荣鑫","id":"9d2a9df435","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陶铸","id":"dbcf15bd08","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"},{"name":"廖承志","id":"f14b64ad68","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"d6430203d0","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"北医长征红卫兵总部、红教工总部"}],"contents":[{"id":"c97594cf88","type":"title","text":"中央首长与“毛泽东思想红卫兵首都兵团”座谈纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d7309010f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你出去了没有？","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb205137ae","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：出去了。（讲了串联情况）我们几个头头每天忙得要死，说不定哪天要下来，大家说我们是小当权派，以后还要斗我们哩！","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32814bd1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"（首长笑了）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a25fc0517","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：领导忙，下面没事干怎么办？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8722ec873e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：整风……其实说整风也没整，以后说准备参加兵团，兵团没要，他们自己组织，这组织那组织。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41a5cb410c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：要哪个组织？要保他们自己。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da0bd0e069","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：希望中央要注意中学情况，中学的问题要抓。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09002fcc0a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：对，我们的责任很大。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3240219fc","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：铁杆红卫兵在中学还是不承认（错误），大学搞了，中学反动路线更深，各个学校组织不多，红五类组织起来……","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d5c9ac0fd","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：什么叫红五类？……（分析干部问题），有些人的父母可能就是黑的。彭小蒙我早就发现她浮躁，她很好，但要批评她。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b74ffae82b","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们根本不是辩论，就是压，只要意见不同，反对反动对联，动手就打。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d7d41b5c2","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这些人只要是拿刀子捅人，就是现行反革命分子，镇压。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02808d9d90","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们认为没有无产阶级专政，就没有无产阶级大民主。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e329a8445","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：对嘛！你们这个观点很好。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bbed7d66ff","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：（对李峰）我不是跟你们讲过，以这为题写一篇吗？","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f5b4955ad","type":"paragraph","text":"李峰：（表示遗憾）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f830285f69","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不要怕，不管他是谁的孩子，什么主席、副主席，将军、部长就甭提了，只要是反革命，就不客气，你们讲嘛，随便讲。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6dd0b0d866","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：红卫兵也应该有自我革命精神，以前只革别人的命，文化革命也要触及自己的灵魂，要造自己灵魂的反。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3aba071454","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：老子革命儿子不一定革命，更何况老子也不一定革命。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77f8cf1199","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（谈到“西纠”镇压革命的活动问题）他们也是红卫兵，对他们不好办。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"27ce1c77f6","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：他们不叫红卫兵，叫纠察队！","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0bb1d9b4d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们要解散我们。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7eceb5693a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我们还要解散他们哩！","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"275198ce25","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们的黑电话随便打，还准备砸我们哩！","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b089fbe7b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：打人的都要把他们抓起来。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f25571d363","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：一辩论他们就要看观点，观点不同就是“混蛋”，就打。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9026ddcf6f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这是流寇！","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f309b2e747","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们只允许同意自己意见，不同意就打、骂。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03b6f05069","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：法西斯罗！希特勒！","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1c3d96274","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：“老子英雄儿好汉，老子反动儿混蛋，基本如此，鬼见愁”，影响极坏。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20618d4d51","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：完全是违背马克思主义的。“老子英雄儿好汉”还是四旧呢！提出对联的人，父亲职位高一点，是个大官，应该搞掉。那天（八月六日）很对立罗！（那对联）我一开始就反对。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86afb6176c","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们要看你的讲话，他们就保密，我们贴了三次，他们撕了三次。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00a452aa3a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：什么？撕的什么？就不对嘛，有的人有有利条件，有幕后操纵者。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad0df30a83","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时李峰给康生同志写了一个条子，问谢清泉是不是谢镗忠的儿子？说他干的两件事。康老递给江青，江青对谢镗忠说：“回去让你的儿子去派出所自首。”）","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfc5bb5ed7","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：那就是老子革命儿混蛋嘛！","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc6cc1905e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：最近确实有一种反扑形势，他们砸其他地方都是坐汽车去的，我们的纠察队也得准备，比较紧张。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68c3c2dac5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们不要把形势估计得那么高，他们只是一小撮，有幕后人，我们帮助你们，你们不要怕，其实他们那么几个人，从东城跑到西城，从西城跑到东城，就那么几辆车。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f50066e7c7","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：现在红卫兵打人都合法了。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79a73e1e65","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不合法，你们帮我们辟谣。说我的什么秘书是张久舜，有人还说李润贵是林彪同志的秘书，我也要造他的反。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8506063b6","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（讲述红卫兵抢东西等恶劣作风。）","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a9eb29833","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这是流寇作风。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cebff0b5e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们为什么这么硬，敢于炮打中央文革？","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74c888a377","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：主要是背后有人。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0308680179","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：不要叫纠察队，（指李峰说）你们的学校，他们真正的秘密的地方，我还没找到。（指六中杀人的红卫兵及西纠队员。）","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62b250d50e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们又发现了一些，其实在校外。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80e1b2700a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：他们在学校呆不住嘛！","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf74458621","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们认为市联络站没有立场，把严肃的阶级斗争看成哄小孩，对谁都一样。（不分多数派，少数派。）","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00d9de12f3","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这个意见对。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a6e1afa788","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我看这个联络站应该解散，就怕打仗，实际支持打。廖承志就是这样，把阶级斗争看成哄小孩，罗青长的孩子现在也打人，现在一个秘书长就了不起了。（面对同学）你们明白，我们是支持你们的，对他们酌情处理。","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de4e560090","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：西城分局的拘留所，西纠的人可以随便出入。……","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e209265f5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我昨天解决了，他们帮了资产阶级专政。","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e44913b9ed","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我认为应该给无缘无故死去的同学平反，平反应该包括这些人，死得要有价值，要死得其所。（首长们连连点头。）","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6aff38f7c3","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：王光华昏死几次，一醒就喊：“要文斗，不要武斗，”坚持党的政策，最后五分钟，给做人工呼吸后，还在喊。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65005360da","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：他是你们应该学习的英雄。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d136636c8e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：他喊“毛主席万岁”了没有？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"592fa08944","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我记不清了，反正“要文斗，不要武斗”我记得清清楚楚。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4b5cc8906","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：他贴第一张反党委的大字报，可以算左派学生。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64b8085d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：对！左派，左派！","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a0fb1095f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他出身算什么？（讲了他出身情况。）","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"822fedd23e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：不算资本家，小业主。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14a69caf18","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不管什么，看他表现嘛！（对同学）救活了吗？","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28a4dd219a","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：说实在的，打人的还有董必武的儿子。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"663483a1dc","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：董福三在哪儿？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c878b0ef2b","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：在广州，听说要办个农场。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"63d3196cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（对姚）要广州军区注意，把他们（董及同伙）叫回来。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06a5bdfe8e","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：那是陶铸抓的。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"784544d939","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：那……管他陶铸呢！","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40278a777c","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：联合行动委员会耍弄中央文革。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7d140ca54","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：六中的红卫兵还要同我们辩论呢？","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9511b3795","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不要理他们，该抓的抓起来，该平反的平反。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84fafd1d0c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你就说，我不同杀人凶手辩论！（气愤）","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb2a007086","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：你们就是要辩论，象谭力夫臭哄哄，你们不要理他，不要同他们辩论，提高他们的身价干什么？你们要正正派派地搞政治，不要学他们搞特务，你们要揭发他们，要有胆量斗争，保证你们的安全，专政。我们帮助你们。我们接见你们晚了，应作自我批评。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8bbfec147d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们特别想见首长。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7bf02284b","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：我们都是老百姓。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e99b5f30c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不要看职位高低，只不过革命工作分工不同。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eab068b313","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：六中教员几十人到国务院要见负责同志，周不让……","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ce49665e2","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：碰到鬼了，你们可以质问周荣鑫：“你究竟支持不支持我们？”你们贴他的大字报，在国务院许明（国务院办公厅秘书处工作，孔原之妻）贴我的大字报，你们可以贴她的。（对康老）康老，她还是你的学生呢？","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18c9184839","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：是啊！你们都是我的学生，“一分为二”嘛！","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d201b732a3","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：许明是我的同学，在外办，她们对你们什么态度？她可能有里通外国的问题呢！你们可以揭发她，没有群众压力，她才不交代呢！","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e314ecfd06","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（编辑部的同学向首长讲印报困难，把三份战报给陈伯达同志，其中谈到《光明日报》印了一次）。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebd0cc3edc","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：穆欣同志可以帮助，解放军应该帮助。（穆欣站起来答应）","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b93f25839","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们《光明日报》印了一下，值得表扬。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5690b1dd37","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们第三期、第四期出版，隔了这么长时间，还没地方印呢！","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85a6fe3cb0","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：穆欣同志有责任，（穆欣解释。）穆欣你虚心点，作自我批评吧！","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37b1099aee","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（又谈到谭力夫的事）","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b450a218c7","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：哎呀！谭力夫那套该上厕所的东西。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25356b5862","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（谈一二·九以前的大反扑形势，又说了打人和暗害事件。）大庆工人代表恨他们，说他们再这样干就……","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e59b3a8a29","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：什么是阶级路线？","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a89b18fce6","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：什么是阶级路线，毛主席的接班人的五个条件就是阶级路线，哪一条也不能少，他们就是不要第四条嘛，专横跋扈，不讲道理嘛！","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b46c70c76d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们干了这么多坏事，公安局也不处理，我认为公安局有问题。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9441096281","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：要把幕后人揪出来就好了，昨天我们解除了他们的武装。公安局是有问题，它起了帮助资产阶级的作用。最近我还听说有一封控告新的公安局的信，……背景是多方面的，多数是犯了路线错误的人。（康生关切地把手帕递给李峰擦眼。）","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d0c57d56d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这些孩子都睡眠不足。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7feb9348e0","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们每天十二点，两点睡觉，有时不睡，外面砸得很厉害，还搞暗害。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8635edbb27","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：他们给你们制造压力了。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b25d853ff6","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：最近，成立那个首都红卫兵联合行动委员会，我校的王昌明说中央文革犯了错误，毛主席不在北京，就象上次派工作组一样。","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"794ee5df2a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：谣言。王昌明是谁的孩子？","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"99216aef7b","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：全总王稼祥的孩子。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f32a7b26ea","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：是个造谣专家吗？","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"080d37b86f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（又提到对联）。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62244b891b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这个对联我看是有人故意提出来的。","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af70a84586","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：有人说中央首长肯定了。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"063bacc848","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：哪个中央？","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7dd7d8f82","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们说是您。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07d6f02a77","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：那次（八·六）他们就很反对我嘛！","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d5ff6ec5f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我认为个对联是由来已久的。一年前，干部子弟传出一句话，说是主席说的，大意是现在有些干部子弟表现不好，而一些剥削阶级子弟表现积极，但政权不交给他们。好多干部子弟把它写在本子上。一年前，从石油附中传来一个材料，平时干部子弟就要联合起来。后来康生在北大表示不同意，说党的阶级政策，在学校不是这样，阶级队伍就是共产党、共青团。我认为阶级路线就是十六条中第五条，解决依靠谁、团结谁、打击谁，阶级政策是为它服务的。刚才同志提到红卫兵内部有修正主义作风，我认为就是有修正主义红卫兵。","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f9af0c711","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：对一组织恐怕要慎重。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb6dcb7e7c","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们说他们在学校受压。","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5bb2e4f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：干部子弟受什么压。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e5d93b0de","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：真正受压的是工农子弟。","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eea40f29b0","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：对，是工农子弟。以后不要叫首长，这是四旧，可叫负责同志。（同学反映方立功式的人物的情况。）","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ab56991b4","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：比较起来是少数，但这些少数要注意。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c864b34da","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：方立功是盗窃犯。","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fe2ee94f9","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：方立功怎么也要受到法律的制裁，就要实行专政，（向阎长贵问方立功父母的情况）抓方立功幕后人，他是董必武加流寇的作法。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97c96f0d5a","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：谭力夫回来了吗？","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fa4e1e78b","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：回来了。谭力夫、方立功都是些小人物。","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ede4a64467","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：谭力夫决不要提，算小人物嘛！谭、方都是小人物。你们要批判王任重，他拖着我们犯错误，王任重给你们搞了，王这个人糟得要死，背着毛主席、背着中央、背着我们小组另搞一套，他得停职反省了。","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4bd648fd3c","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（谈到几个纵队）。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a77dd1aebc","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：八一纵队负责人是谁？","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab2bfb098f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：赖锐锐。","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97bf7fc8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：可以抓了。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"01e70768bc","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：学校的同学至今不敢组织起来，压得厉害。","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f4987db75","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：压力，无形的压力。","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b0f49f95d","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：对，无形的压力。关于军训我不同意，我希望中学要大干一场，乱，好多问题还没办嘛？路线斗争要搞（延长两天）。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd66c2a2ed","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：刚反一个军训，集训，又来一个军训。","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"edcfba13d7","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：看来最近还要暗害呢！如六中九月末还打死一个同学，我比较了解。（叙述惨害经过。）","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"374b2301b5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：救活了吗？","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8bff3038e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：活了。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c546f031d","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：被杀就因为他“变节”？","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d9c9d2058","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：怀疑他揭发了西纠。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d2d5aa19b5","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：都是革干子弟，他们无法无天了。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e1927a0e2","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：没办法。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4a80e3357","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不怕，不怕，我们帮助你们。西纠大头目叫孔丹，他父母都有问题。","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52049e0fcf","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：六中的教员要求中央接见，因周荣鑫不让。","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"925c634ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：这可能。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3cdfb8c89e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：（谈到纠察队）","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b99cecbee2","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不要叫纠察队，这个名字好象凌驾一切，我们不要这样一批人，你们可以叫另外的，多做宣传工作。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a716f92b51","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：他们不光是唯成份论，也是唯观点论，观点不同也打也骂。","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12c6edc7dc","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：唯观点论，我们倒是要唯观点论。唯毛泽东思想观点论。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47dde468c9","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：红卫兵是否是阶级队伍，他们总说红卫兵是阶级队伍。","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ad5086765d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：不是，它那能高于党，他是青年学生的一种革命组织，你不能说修正主义分子，作为一个组织不是这样。有分子是修正主义分子，说修正主义红卫兵不好，这个组织在国际影响很大。（同学谈到阶级路线。）","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b56303587","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：阶级社会要讲成份，这是本质，但要看到无产阶级和资产阶级都有背叛其本阶级的人，这就是不要唯成份，重在政治表现。","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9198a148ae","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：其他劳动人民子弟，可不可以组织红卫兵？","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06c5d3efa9","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：可以。怎么不可以？！只要是干革命就好嘛！","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55f251e4f9","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们是提着脑袋干革命的，随时都准备着死！","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dde711d75d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：干么要死，要活嘛，干革命！","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4687cdd8e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们希望解放军帮助我们搞军训。","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e910326cc6","type":"paragraph","text":"另一同学：我不同意，中学运动必须大乱，刚刚搞起来，又要搞军训，等于阻止批判资产阶级反动路线。","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8518e85ab4","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：军训有战备意义。","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21a23bd169","type":"paragraph","text":"另一同学：无产阶级文化大革命就是最好的战备。","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e4a4c1f0b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在一切服从文化大革命，这最重要，我的意见不派，派不是好办法。","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26bb2f50d0","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：总理讲过。江青：什么时候？同学：十一月九日。","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aafca78b2b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：那天他还生气，西纠打了解放军记者，可能就讲了，我们不是这样。","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47e177b665","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：十五期社论讲到一个特点，就是工人起来闹革命，学生和工人，我们要不要到工厂去？","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f78dd8232f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：暂时不去工厂，可以先到住宅区嘛！要一步一步嘛！","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"096a845024","type":"paragraph","text":"北医长征红卫兵总部、红教工总部","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"006c0bc054","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}